headline: U.S. Bancorp (USB) Stock Trades Up, Here Is Why
summary: Shares of financial services giant U.S. Bancorp (NYSE:USB) jumped 3.2% in the morning session after an analyst at Barclays raised the price target on the company's stock to $65 from $56.
